OUR COMMITMENT TO YOU
---------------------
We will handle all financial matters with the utmost care and sensitivity. There is no rush - we will work at your pace and be available whenever you need us.

WHAT WE WILL HELP WITH
----------------------
* Account Transfers - Retitling assets to beneficiaries or estate
* Required Distributions - Managing IRA and retirement account RMDs
* Tax Coordination - Working with estate attorneys and CPAs
* Beneficiary Claims - Life insurance and annuity death benefits
* Ongoing Management - Continued advisory services for surviving family members

DOCUMENTS WE WILL NEED (when you're ready)
------------------------------------------
- Certified Death Certificate (multiple copies recommended)
- Letters Testamentary or Letters of Administration
- Trust documents (if applicable)
- Beneficiary identification

